AddressInfo.Title: High School Yards
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Bay for use of City Car Club Only
*Please note that there is only two parking spaces available for charging your vehicle at this site.* This is a publicly available charging point within a University of Edinburgh Car Park. There is no requirement to display a permit when parked within the designated bay AND charging. Vehicle must be charging. 4 hour maximum stay. Available 24 hours a day 365 days a year. If gates to High School Yards are closed please contact University of Edinburgh Security on 0131 650 2257.
